{"tid":2047450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警一哥，比卡超等高官陪同林鄭聽日去北京講述香港人對國安法意見","createTime":"2020-06-02T06:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T10:13:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":22,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"12875b502a95ac689b751e891c13136892906e76","tid":2047450,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥明日（六月三日）訪問北京。全國人民代表大會常務委員會將制定建立健全香港特別行政區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制的相關法律，中央政府將就此聽取林鄭月娥的意見。律政司司長鄭若驊資深大律師、保安局局長李家超、警務處處長鄧炳強及行政長官辦公室主任陳國基將會隨行。 林鄭月娥將於今日傍晚前往深圳，翌日上午轉往北京，同日晚上返回深圳，並於六月四日早上回港。她離港期間，由政務司司長張建宗署理行政長官職務。<br />\n<br />\n【最新】行政長官林鄭月娥與多名主要官員明日訪京，中央聽取其對港區國安法立法的意見<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=17129&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D17129%26refer%3DShare&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=d591e7ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D17129%26refer%3DShare&h=0ad280ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=17129&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"5df8fd58a5712aafa0bdc706c7a3338eda986108","tid":2047450,"uid":76745,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:22:56.000Z","msg":"係咪坐737max?"},{"pid":"98f1375279823cbe9ef6cbd4a1d7901ca843d775","tid":2047450,"uid":214173,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"又被支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af45026b883a06c8226749a5f5918d83b44ed1f6","tid":2047450,"uid":36567,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"好行唔送<br />\n估到唔會係好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b44276da1742feab23e596cfde6f4bb5bbf80b","tid":2047450,"uid":35914,"like":80,"dislike":2,"score":78,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"飛機失事,唔該"},{"